text: Monique Rossi (born 16 December 1937) is a French gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Montceau-les-Mines
